{"tid":1728080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 17/11 願祢榮光歸香港 + 東歐巨變30周年集會","createTime":"2019-11-16T17:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:33:38.000Z","uid":310883,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f0b11a19ba3b4cf34e59522b048c6345bd5cc3","tid":1728080,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"首先，大家一睇個活動主題同內容，一定會feel到一陣膠味濃既感覺，尤其係東歐巨變30周年集會，人地一早有晒民主，無啦啦搞個集會，又砌牆又推牆，成浸「平反六四」集會既膠味出晒嚟。甚至覺得呢場集會同以家香港無咩關係。<br />\n但唔該大家諗下，做咩搞手無啦啦會搞個咁既集會，因為直接以香港局部反警暴、五大訴求等做主題，黑狗係一定唔撚批既，搞手就係擺到明用其他主題申請nono返嚟，然後等我地騎劫返個集會。<br />\n所以唔該唔好浪費搞手既心機，難得申請到集會不反對通知書，如果聽日下午無咩突發事發生，就好應該趁聽日呢次機會去，圍結返一定人數出嚟，至少可以同到大家講我地從來冇離開過大家。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無論你覺得自己係勇武、花生撚、和理非咩都好，行動要be water，心態都要be water，聽日既活動一定要有返咁上下人到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(上次消防救護打氣集會先得1000個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n利申: 預咗比人屌集中撚，實會有人話上次11.2維園唔夠10分鐘就放TG趕人。但我想講即使佢10分鐘放，5分鐘又好，我地都唔可以縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n11月16日駐軍法已經徹底滅亡，無險可守，各位聽日唔好再休息，企一企出來可以嗎? 曬冷數人頭就係最好既民意證明。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhykpqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhykpqC.jpg&h=b8c1196e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwdo6DS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frwdo6DS.jpg&h=4c7ad834&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔信基督教既可以2pm直接去愛丁堡幫手砌牆，否則建議去完第一個活動再去第二個活動。</span></span>"},{"pid":"032e5391fcc25276de45217dd670f6486a738bf4","tid":1728080,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b4a8564d3a3d4041aea70540912ff53915d698","tid":1728080,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"和理非全面進場<br />\n行動要be water 心態都要be water<br />\n和勇不分 既可和亦可勇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f14d9bf81bafeb276bb6e262d115193a1954ee1","tid":1728080,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"pish 行動"},{"pid":"916e9c5e52aac522c9a2f6bd2d661bac250af76d","tid":1728080,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"87eaf56b926b2e8134e4eb90f47190f135432226","tid":1728080,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f14d9bf81bafeb276bb6e262d115193a1954ee1","tid":1728080,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"pish 行動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9476bc4bbeee19544ad2b6b29d9257be184877b9","tid":1728080,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a58ac31d63e4fa78c2c4f7bcd929baf8d9